%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Behind%20Priyanka%20Gandhi's%20'No'%20To%20Poll%20Fight%2C%20A%20Recurring%20BJP%20Taunt%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress's%20announcement%20of%20candidates%20for%20its%20two%20prestige%20seats%2C%20Amethi%20and%20Rae%20Bareli%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20has%20effectively%20put%20the%20lid%20on%20speculation%20regarding%20senior%20party%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra's%20electoral%20debut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%20in%20the%20party%2C%20Congress%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20had%20requested%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20to%20contest%20from%20Amethi%20or%20Rae%20Bareli%2C%20but%20she%20refused.%20Behind%20her%20reluctance%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20victory%20for%20her%20and%20her%20brother%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20would%20put%20three%20members%20of%20the%20Gandhi%20family%20in%20Parliament%20--%20mother%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20is%20now%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20This%20would%20reinforce%20the%20BJP's%20charge%20of%20dynastic%20politics%2C%20she%20reasoned%2C%20according%20to%20sources%20in%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20leaders%2C%20however%2C%20fear%20that%20her%20decision%20may%20create%20a%20negative%20perception%20among%20voters.%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20has%20been%20campaigning%20extensively%20and%20has%20been%20the%20face%20of%20the%20Congress's%20counterstrike%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20'mangalsutra'%20charge%20at%20the%20Grand%20Old%20party.%20Many%20feel%20that%20the%20Congress%20could%20have%20benefited%20from%20her%20star%20power%20if%20she%20contested%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress's%20much-awaited%20decision%20on%20these%20two%20seats%20came%20early%20this%20morning.%20A%20big%20surprise%20was%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20being%20fielded%20from%20Rae%20Bareli%2C%20and%20not%20Amethi%2C%20which%20he%20has%20represented%20thrice%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%20For%20Amethi%2C%20the%20Congress%20chose%20Kishori%20Lal%20Sharma%2C%20a%20long-time%20loyalist%20of%20the%20Gandhis.%20Mr%20Sharma%2C%20who%20has%20earlier%20worked%20as%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%20representative%20in%20Rae%20Bareli%2C%20will%20be%20contesting%20his%20first%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20is%20also%20contesting%20from%20Kerala's%20Wayanad%2C%20and%20Mr%20Sharma%20will%20be%20filing%20their%20nomination%20today.%20Amethi%20and%20Rae%20Bareli%20will%20vote%20in%20the%20fifth%20phase%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20on%20May%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20will%20take%20on%20the%20BJP's%20Dinesh%20Pratap%20Singh%20in%20Rae%20Bareli%20and%20Mr%20Sharma%20is%20up%20against%20Union%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20in%20Amethi.%20Ms%20Irani%20had%20scored%20a%20shock%20win%20against%20Mr%20Gandhi%20in%20the%202019%20polls%20and%20has%20been%20campaigning%20extensively%20in%20the%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leaders%20are%20confident%20that%20Mr%20Gandhi%20will%20post%20a%20thumping%20win%20in%20Rae%20Bareli.%20For%20Amethi%2C%20they%20say%20that%20Mr%20Sharma%20is%20a%20grassroots%20leader%20who%20will%20perform%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20took%20to%20social%20media%20to%20extend%20her%20greetings%20to%20Mr%20Sharma.%20%26quot%3BKishori%20Lal%20Sharma%20shares%20a%20bond%20with%20our%20family.%20He%20has%20been%20dedicated%20to%20serving%20the%20people%20of%20Amethi%20and%20Rae%20Bareli.%20His%20zeal%20for%20public%20service%20is%20an%20example%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20heartening%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20named%20him%20its%20candidate%20from%20Amethi.%20His%20dedication%20and%20sense%20of%20duty%20will%20surely%20bring%20him%20success%20in%20this%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20taken%20a%20swipe%20at%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20over%20the%20Congress's%20move%20to%20switch%20him%20from%20Amethi%20to%20Rae%20Bareli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParty%20spokesperson%20Jaiveer%20Shergill%20said%20the%20Congress%20is%20now%20%26quot%3Baddicted%20to%20daydreaming%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi's%20decision%20to%20not%20contest%20in%20Amethi%20shows%20that%20the%20Congress%20campaigns%20lacks%20confidence.%20Instead%20of%20leading%20the%20fight%20like%20a%20responsible%20general%2C%20he%20is%20behaving%20like%20a%20runaway%20soldier%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714714860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fjfcob5pg_priyanka-gandhi-vadra_625x300_03_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpriyanka-gandhi-vadra-2024-lok-sabha-election-why-priyanka-gandhi-refused-poll-fight-despite-mallikarjun-kharges-request-5577461%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress's%20announcement%20of%20candidates%20for%20its%20two%20prestige%20seats%2C%20Amethi%20and%20Rae%20Bareli%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20has%20effectively%20put%20the%20lid%20on%20speculation%20regarding%20senior%20party%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra's%20electoral%20debut.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpriyanka-gandhi-vadra-2024-lok-sabha-election-why-priyanka-gandhi-refused-poll-fight-despite-mallikarjun-kharges-request-5577461%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpriyanka-gandhi-vadra-2024-lok-sabha-election-why-priyanka-gandhi-refused-poll-fight-despite-mallikarjun-kharges-request-5577461%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpriyanka-gandhi-vadra-2024-lok-sabha-election-why-priyanka-gandhi-refused-poll-fight-despite-mallikarjun-kharges-request-5577461%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20tornado%20hit%20an%20Oklahoma%20newsroom%20built%20in%20the%201920s.%20The%20damage%20isn't%20stopping%20the%20presses%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714714695000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109805263%2Cimgsize-213892.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fa-tornado-hit-an-oklahoma-newsroom-built-in-the-1920s-the-damage-isnt-stopping-the-presses%2Farticleshow%2F109805263.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109805263.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESulphur%20suffered%20Oklahoma's%20worst%20destruction%20during%20an%20outreak%20of%20severe%20weather%20when%20a%20tornado%20plowed%20through%20downtown%20in%20the%20community%20of%20about%205%2C000%20residents%20south%20of%20Oklahoma%20City.%20Four%20people%20were%20killed%20across%20the%20state%2C%20including%20a%20woman%20who%20was%20in%20a%20bar%20near%20the%20newspaper's%20offices.%20Kathy%20John's%20husband%2C%20James%20John%2C%20joined%20the%20staff%20in%201968%2C%20after%20his%20father%20ran%20it%20for%2027%20years.%20Together%2C%20the%20pair%20have%20been%20covering%20Sulphur%2C%20the%20county%20seat%2C%20for%20more%20than%2050%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fa-tornado-hit-an-oklahoma-newsroom-built-in-the-1920s-the-damage-isnt-stopping-the-presses%2Farticleshow%2F109805263.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fa-tornado-hit-an-oklahoma-newsroom-built-in-the-1920s-the-damage-isnt-stopping-the-presses%2Famp_articleshow%2F109805263.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fa-tornado-hit-an-oklahoma-newsroom-built-in-the-1920s-the-damage-isnt-stopping-the-presses%2Famp_articleshow%2F109805263.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Highways%20Authority%20Planning%20To%20Build%20Self-Healing%20Roads%20In%20India%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Highways%20Authority%20of%20India%20(NHAI)%20is%20planning%20to%20introduce%20a%20revolutionary%20technology%20for%20road%20maintenance%20in%20the%20country.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDDNewsHindi%2Fstatus%2F1786016539545633004%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDD%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20This%20technology%20will%20enable%20a%20road%20to%20'repair'%20itself%20using%20a%20new%20type%20of%20asphalt.%20This%20material%20will%20be%20infused%20with%20steel%20fibre%20and%20bitumen.%20If%20a%20gap%20emerges%20on%20the%20road%2C%20the%20bitumen%20will%20spread%20to%20cover%20it%20and%20along%20with%20steel%20threads%2C%20fill%20the%20potholes.%20NHAI%20official%20say%20it%20will%20fix%20the%20persistent%20problem%20of%20potholes%2C%20a%20major%20contributor%20to%20road%20accidents%20and%20fatalities%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%2C%20however%2C%20not%20known%20how%20long%20the%20asphalt%20will%20take%20to%20cover%20and%20'repair'%20a%20pothole%20or%20gap%20in%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20considering%20ingenious%20and%20unconventional%20methods%20to%20improve%20durability%20and%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20potholes%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Findustry%2Ftransportation%2Froadways%2Fself-healing-roads-may-soon-be-a-reality-nhai%2Farticleshow%2F109671277.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20quoted%20a%20senior%20government%20official%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20government%20will%20undertake%20cost-benefit%20analysis%20of%20the%20project%20before%20giving%20a%20go-ahead.%20NHAI%20is%20confident%20that%20the%20new%20technology%20will%20increase%20the%20lifespan%20of%20roads%20and%20minimise%20traffic%20disruption%20caused%20by%20potholes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsphalt%20is%20a%20sustainable%20paving%20material%20used%20for%20constructing%20pavements%20and%20highways%2C%20along%20with%20airport%20runways%2C%20parking%20lots%20and%20driveways.%20Asphalt%20ultimately%20speeds%20construction%2C%20is%20environmentally%20friendly%2C%20and%20provides%20a%20smooth%20and%20quiet%20ride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20made%20by%20a%20mixture%20of%20aggregates%2C%20binder%20and%20filler.%20Aggregates%20are%20mixed%20with%20bitumen%20to%20create%20a%20durable%20and%20reliable%20mixture.%20Specialised%20trucks%20or%20transporters%20deliver%20the%20hot%20asphalt%20mixture%20to%20the%20desired%20location%2C%20where%20it%20is%20spread%20and%20compacted%20using%20heavy%20machinery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20over%20long%20period%20of%20time%2C%20bitumen%20deteriorates%2C%20leading%20to%20erosion%20of%20the%20asphalt%20and%20the%20formation%20of%20cracks%2C%20which%20eventually%20evolve%20into%20hazardous%20potholes.%20The%20new%20technology%20aims%20to%20tackle%20this%20degradation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENHAI%20is%20a%20government%20agency%20responsible%20for%20construction%20and%20management%20of%20road%20network%20of%20national%20highways%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714714680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2F9q9l6rvg_india-national-highways-india-expressways-ani_625x300_27_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhighways-authority-planning-to-build-self-healing-roads-in-india-report-5577951%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20will%20undertake%20cost-benefit%20analysis%20of%20the%20project%20before%20giving%20a%20go-ahead.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhighways-authority-planning-to-build-self-healing-roads-in-india-report-5577951%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhighways-authority-planning-to-build-self-healing-roads-in-india-report-5577951%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv