%20from%20Raebareli%20--%20which%20she%20had%20nursed%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20on%20her%20mother's%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20candidates%20will%20file%20their%20papers%20today%20--%20the%20last%20day%20for%20filing%20nominations%20for%20the%20fifth%20phase%20of%20election%20on%20May%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20decision%20was%20announced%20on%20Friday%20after%20weeks%20of%20suspense.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20concern%20that%20the%20switch%20of%20seat%20for%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20could%20play%20into%20BJP%20hands%2C%20given%20Union%20minister%20Smriti%20Irani's%20victory%20of%202019%20in%20Amethi.%20The%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20is%20all%20set%20to%20defend%20the%20seat%20and%20has%20declared%20that%20the%20Congress%20delay%20was%20the%20result%20of%20cold%20feet%2C%20in%20view%20of%20her%20imminent%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20she%20said%20the%20leadership%20%26quot%3Bis%20aware%20that%20this%20is%20a%20losing%20seat%20for%20them%2C%20because%20if%20they%20were%20so%20confident%20of%20their%20victory%2C%20they%20would%20have%20announced%20their%20candidate%20by%20now%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Vadra's%20decision%20not%20to%20contest%20could%20add%20to%20the%20party's%20discomfiture.%20Many%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%20suspect%20that%20it%20could%20create%20a%20negative%20perception%20that%20may%20add%20reflect%20on%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20election%20across%20the%20country.%20Polling%20on%20353%20seats%20is%20still%20left%2C%20of%20which%20the%20Congress%20is%20contesting%20on%20330%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20Ms%20Vadra's%20reluctance%20stemmed%20from%20the%20fact%20that%20her%20victory%20from%20Raebareli%20could%20reinforce%20the%20BJP%20allegations%20of%20dynasty%20politics%2C%20since%20all%20three%20of%20them%20would%20be%20in%20parliament.%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20is%20already%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%