p%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Gandhi%20won%20the%20seat%20in%201990%2C%20but%20after%20his%20death%20in%20an%20air%20crash%20that%20year%20led%20to%20bypolls%20in%201981.%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20got%20the%20seat%20and%20won%20it%20four%20times%20until%20his%20assassination%20in%201991.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20chose%20Satish%20Sharma%20to%20contest%20the%20bypolls%20and%20won%20it.%20Mr%20Sharma%20went%20on%20to%20win%20it%20for%20a%20second%20time%20in%201996%2C%20but%20fell%20short%20of%20votes%20in%201998.%20BJP%20won%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20general%20elections%20a%20year%20later%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20clinched%20it%20back%20from%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20passed%20it%20over%20to%20son%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20Mr%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20would%20go%20on%20to%20head%20the%20Congress%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20won%20the%20seat%20in%202004%2C%202009%2C%20and%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20he%20lost%20to%20the%20BJP's%20Smriti%20Irani%2C%20now%20a%20Union%20minister%2C%20but%20remained%20an%20MP%20by%20winning%20a%20second%20seat%20in%20Kerala%20-%20Wayanad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20years%20since%2C%20Mr%20Gandhi%20re-contested%20the%20Wayanad%20seat%20amid%20speculations%20that%20he%20might%20try%20to%20win%20Amethi%20back%20too.%20But%20the%20Congress%20had%20other%20plans.%20It%20has%20fielded%20Kishori%20Lal%20Sharma%20from%20the%20seat%2C%20while%20offering%20Raebareli%20-%20the%20only%20seat%20held%20by%20the%20Congress%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20-%20to%20Mr%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gandhi%20will%20now%20be%20contesting%20from%20the%20seat%20his%20mother%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20has%20represented%20for%20five%20consecutive%20terms%20since%202004%20until%20she%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20And%20after%2026%20years%2C%20his%20Amethi%20seat%20will%20see%20a%20non-Gandhi%20fighting%20to%20keep%20the%20Congress%20flag%20flying%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714710420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.