0and%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20things%20in%20life%20that%20might%20sound%20like%20good%20ideas%2C%20but%20they're%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Vergara%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Fsofia-vergara-beautiful-issue-cover-story-8633965%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeople%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20January%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BGriselda%26quot%3B%20star%20said%20her%20marriage%20to%20Joe%20Manganiello%20ended%20because%20he%20wanted%20kids%2C%20but%20she%20didn't.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsofia-vergara-looks-body-opened-doors-for-her-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESofia%20Vergara%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2051%2C%20says%20she%20doesn't%20want%20more%20kids%20at%20her%20age%20because%20she%20can't%20give%20them%20her%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20think%20because%20of%20my%20career%2C%20the%20way%20I%20live%20my%20life%2C%20the%20way%20my%20marriage%20was%2C%20that%20it%20was%20fair%20to%20bring%20a%20kid%20to%20this%20world%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20be%20able%20to%20give%20100%20percent%2C%26quot%3B%20Vergara%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Fsofia-vergara-beautiful-issue-cover-story-8633965%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeople%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Vergara%20was%20already%20a%20mother%2C%20she%20knew%20the%20kind%20of%20dedication%20it%20would%20take%20to%20raise%20another%20child%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20she%20couldn't%20provide%20at%20this%20point%20in%20her%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20things%20in%20life%20that%20might%20sound%20like%20good%20ideas%2C%20but%20they're%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20Vergara%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20know%20what%20it%20means%20to%20be%20a%20good%20mother%20or%20to%20try%20to%20be%20the%20best%20mother%20that%20you%20can%2C%20and%20that%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20sacrifices%2C%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20energy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20ad