%20policy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20India%2C%20we%20reconstructed%20the%20material%20based%20on%20the%20correspondence%20with%20other%20files.%20We%20sought%20another%20copy%20of%20the%20transcript%2C%20but%20Israel%20never%20provided%20it.%20There%20can't%20be%20a%20more%20glaring%20instance%20of%20how%20politics%20plays%20out%20in%20sharing%20intelligence%20between%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20that%20point%2C%20India%20was%20critical%2C%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20wasn't%20disintegrated%20and%20India%20was%20a%20backchannel%20between%20the%20US%20and%20the%20Soviets.%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20was%20part%20of%20that%20communication%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20mentioned%20during%20the%20discussion%20which%20was%20also%20attended%20by%20two%20Israeli%20security%20experts%2C%20Joseph%20Rozen%20and%20Kobe%20Michael%2C%20the%20latter%20having%20served%20as%20Deputy%20Director%20General%20and%20head%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20division%20in%20the%20Israeli%20Ministry%20of%20Strategic%20Affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Verma%20said%20that%20such%20incidents%20have%20happened%20whenever%20global%20equations%20are%20changing%20or%20the%20existing%20order%20is%20challenged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20particular%20transcript%20effectively%20said%20that%20the%20payment%20had%20been%20made...%20It%20said%20that%20'Godman'%20has%20made%20the%20payment...%20What%20could%20be%20more%20obvious...%20On%20the%20backchannel%2C%20all%20this%20information%20was%20documented%20and%20our%20intelligence%20agencies%20were%20aware%20of%20that.%20They%20asked%20for%20security%20to%20be%20provided%20which%20the%20government%20of%20the%20day%20did%20not%20provide%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20expert%20told%20the%20virtual%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714708560000%2C%22visual