's%20stern%20response%20came%20after%20Pakistan's%20UN%20envoy%20Munir%20Akram%20made%20lengthy%20remarks%20against%20India%2C%20including%20references%20to%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20and%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20during%20his%20address%20to%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20meeting%20on%20%E2%80%98Culture%20of%20Peace.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20final%20point%E2%80%A6in%20this%20Assembly%2C%20as%20we%20endeavour%20to%20cultivate%20a%20culture%20of%20peace%20amid%20these%20challenging%20times%2C%20our%20focus%20remains%20steadfast%20on%20constructive%20dialogue.%20We%20thus%20choose%20to%20set%20aside%20the%20remarks%20from%20a%20certain%20delegation%2C%20which%20not%20only%20lack%20decorum%20but%20also%20detract%20from%20our%20collective%20efforts%20due%20to%20their%20destructive%20and%20pernicious%20nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ms%20Kamboj%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20strongly%20encourage%20that%20delegation%20to%20align%20with%20the%20central%20principles%20of%20respect%20and%20diplomacy%20that%20must%20always%20guide%20our%20discussions.%20Or%20is%20that%20too%20much%20to%20ask%20of%20a%20country%20that%20harbours%20a%20most%20dubious%20track%20record%20on%20all%20aspects%20in%20itself%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Kamboj%20asserted%20that%20terrorism%20stands%20in%20direct%20opposition%20to%20the%20culture%20of%20peace%20and%20the%20core%20teachings%20of%20all%20religions%2C%20which%20advocate%20compassion%2C%20understanding%20and%20coexistence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20sows%20discord%2C%20breeds%20hostility%20and%20undermines%20the%20universal%20values%20of%20respect%20and%20harmony%20that%20underpin%20cultural%20and%20religious%20traditions%20worldwide.%20It%20is%20essential%20for%20Member%20States%20to%20work%20together%20actively%20to%20nurture%20a%20genuine%20culture%20of%20peace%20and%20to%20view%20the%20world%20as%20a%20united%20family%2C%20as%20my%20country%20strongly%20believes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Kamboj%20further%20said%20that%20the%20world%20faces%20significant%20challenges%20from%20geopolitical%20tensions%20and%20uneven%20development.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20growing%20intolerance%2C%20discrimination%20and%20violence%20based%20on%20religion%20or%20belief%20indeed%20demand%20our%20urgent%20attention%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20particularly%20concerned%20by%20the%20escalating%20attacks%20on%20sacred%20sites%2C%20including%20churches%2C%20monasteries%2C%20gurudwaras%2C%20mosques%2C%20temples%20and%20synagogues%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20such%20acts%20require%20a%20swift%20and%20united%20response%20from%20the%20global%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20crucial%20that%20our%20discussions%20therefore%20forthrightly%20address%20these%20issues%2C%20resisting%20political%20expediencies.%20We%20must%20tackle%20these%20challenges%20directly%20and%20ensure%20that%20they%20are%20central%20to%20our%20policy%2C%20dialogues%20and%20international%20engagements%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Kamboj%20told%20the%20UNGA%20meeting%20that%20the%20doctrine%20of%20Ahimsa%20championed%20by%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20bedrock%20of%20India's%20commitment%20to%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20not%20only%20the%20birthplace%20of%20Hinduism%2C%20Buddhism%2C%20Jainism%20and%20Sikhism%2C%20but%20also%20a%20stronghold%20for%20Islam%2C%20Judaism%2C%20Christianity%20and%20Zoroastrianism.%20It%20has%20historically%20been%20a%20refuge%20for%20persecuted%20faiths%2C%20illustrating%20its%20long-standing%20embrace%20of%20diversity%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20its%20remarkable%20religious%20and%20linguistic%20diversity%2C%20India's%20cultural%20mosaic%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20tolerance%20and%20coexistence.%20Festivals%20such%20as%20Diwali%2C%20Eid%2C%20Christmas%20and%20Nowruz%20transcend%20religious%20boundaries%2C%20celebrating%20shared%20joys%20among%20diverse%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ms%20Kamboj%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20commended%20Bangladesh%20for%20presenting%20the%20resolution%20%E2%80%98Follow-up%20to%20the%20Declaration%20and%20Programme%20of%20Action%20on%20a%20Culture%20of%20Peace'%2C%20which%20Delhi%20%E2%80%9Cproudly%26quot%3B%20co-sponsored.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1714707060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fj2thh0g4_ruchira-kamboj-india-permanent-representative-to-the-un-ambassador-ani_625x300_16_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-at-un-general-assembly-pakistan-harbours-most-dubious-track-record-on-all-aspects-5577220%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20sharp%20retort%2C%20India%20has%20said%20Pakistan%20harbours%20a%20%26quot%3Bmost%20dubious%20track%20record%26quot%3B%20on%20all%20aspects%2C%20as%20it%20slammed%20%26quot%3Bdestructive%20and%20pernicious%26quot%3B%20remarks%20made%20by%20Islamabad's%20envoy%20in%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20here.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-at-un-general-assembly-pakistan-harbours-most-dubious-track-record-on-all-aspects-5577220%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-at-un-general-assembly-pakistan-harbours-most-dubious-track-record-on-all-aspects-5577220%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-at-un-general-assembly-pakistan-harbours-most-dubious-track-record-on-all-aspects-5577220%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHospitality%2C%20Then%20Goodbye%26quot%3B%3A%20J%20Scindia%20To%20Congress%20Leaders%20Campaigning%20In%20MP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20minister%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%2C%20facing%20his%20first%20election%20from%20home%20turf%20Guna%20after%20shifting%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20appeared%20quite%20at%20ease%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail.%20%26quot%3BPolitics%20and%20elections%20are%20not%20an%20end%20for%20us.%20it%20is%20a%20beginning%20to%20take%20forward%20the%20practice%20of%20service%20to%20people%2C'%20he%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20of%20%26quot%3BMaharaj%26quot%3B%20--%20as%20the%20erstwhile%20royal%20is%20known%20across%20the%20area%20-%20has%20been%20representing%20the%20constituency%20since%201950s.%20His%20grandmother%20Vijayaraje%20Scindia%20and%20his%20father%20Madhavrao%20Scindia%20were%20both%20MPs%20from%20whichever%20party%20they%20represented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Scindia%20contested%20his%20first%20election%20in%202002%20after%20the%20death%20of%20his%20father%2C%20and%20has%20been%20a%20four-time%20MP%20from%20the%20seat%20--%20till%20he%20lost%20to%20the%20BJP's%20KP%20Singh%20Yadav%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20his%20key%20opponent%20is%20Congress's%20Yadvendra%20Yadav%2C%20the%20son%20of%20BJP%20leader%20Rao%20Deshraj%20Singh%20Yadav%2C%20who%20was%20a%20three-time%20legislator%20from%20Mungaoli.%20The%20Congress%20strategy%20is%20to%20consolidate%20the%20Yadav%20vote%2C%20which%20had%20paid%20off%20for%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Yadavs%20comprise%20a%20chunk%20of%20Guna's%20population%20and%20are%20expected%20to%20account%20for%20around%20250%2C000%20votes.%20On%20the%20rare%20occasions%20the%20constituency%20has%20chosen%20a%20non-Scindia%20to%20represent%20them%2C%20the%20candidate%20belonged%20to%20the%20Yadav%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Yadav%20community's%20heft%20has%20been%20reflected%20in%20the%20BJP's%20choice%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20this%20time.%20In%20March%2C%20after%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20was%20announced%2C%20Mohan%20Yadav%20had%20led%20a%20Yadav%20community%20meeting%20where%20Mr%20Scindia%20was%20also%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20appeared%20unperturbed%20by%20the%20Congress%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20constituency%20everyone%20belongs%20to%20me%20and%20I%20belong%20to%20everyone.%20The%20Scindias%20have%20never%20contested%20elections%20on%20basis%20of%20caste%20and%20creed.%20And%20we%20have%20contested%20against%20candidates%20from%20every%20community.%20It%20is%20upto%20a%20party%20which%20candidate%20they%20choose%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20coming%20to%20campaign%20for%20the%20Congress%20candidate%2C%20Mr%20Scindia%20-%20known%20to%20be%20close%20to%20the%20Gandhis%20before%20his%20crossover%20to%20the%20BJP%20-%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BAny%20leader%20can%20come%2C%20we%20provide%20them%20hospitality%20under%20the%20%3Cem%3EAtithi%20Devo%20Bhava%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Guests%20are%20gods)%20maxim.%20We%20provide%20them%20hospitality%20and%20after%20that%2C%20bid%20them%20goodbye%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Mr%20Scindia%2C%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Uma%20Bharati%20had%20hit%20the%20campaign%20trail%20last%20week.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20time%20she%20took%20part%20in%20the%20current%20election%20campaign%20after%20being%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bbreak%20from%20politics%26quot%3B.%20for%20about%20four%20months.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20my%20good%20fortune.%20She%20is%20my%20aunt%20and%20has%20given%20me%20her%20blessings%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Scindia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20chances%20of%20Digvijaya%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20contesting%20from%20neighbouring%20Raigarh%2C%20Mr%20Scindia%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20is%20bankrupt%20in%20terms%20of%20ideology%20and%20its%20human%20resources.%