%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump's%20hush-money%20trial%20has%20always%20had%20the%20National%20Enquirer%20as%20its%20flashy%20backdrop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Thursday's%20testimony%20was%20so%20chock-a-block%20with%20talk%20of%20C-list%20celebrity%20sex%20tapes%20and%20rehab%20scoops%2C%20it%20was%20as%20if%20the%20supermarket%20tabloid%20had%20somehow%20engulfed%20the%20proceeding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECharlie%20Sheen%2C%20Hulk%20Hogan%2C%20Lindsay%20Lohan%2C%20Floyd%20Mayweather%2C%20Tila%20Tequila%20%E2%80%94%20all%20were%20name-dropped%20in%20morning%20testimony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20explains%20their%20cameo%20appearances%20on%20week%20two%20of%20testimony%20in%20the%20only-ever%20criminal%20trial%20of%20a%20current%20or%20former%20president%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETurns%20out%20each%20has%20had%20a%20run-in%20with%20attorney%20Keith%20Davidson%2C%20a%20key%20prosecution%20witness%20who%20repped%20both%20former%20Playboy%20Bunny%20Karen%20McDougal%20and%20porn%20star%20Stormy%20Daniels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManhattan%20prosecutors%20say%20that%20Trump%20falsified%2034%20business%20records%20in%20order%20to%20hide%20an%20illegal%2C%20election-influencing%2C%202016%20hush-money%20payment%20to%20Daniels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20direct%2C%20Davidson%20told%20jurors%20how%20both%20women%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhush-money-texts-reveal-tawdry-bidding-war-porn-star-bunny-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epursued%20catch-and-kill%20cash%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Enquirer%20for%20their%20tales%20of%20sex%20with%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Trump%20attorney%20Emil%20Bove%20went%20on%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20court%20sketch%20shows%20Donald%20Trump%20sitting%20in%20court%20alongside%20Emil%20Bove.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6618442516bde8d4ead8204a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDonald%20Trump%20at%20the%20defense%20table%20in%20his%20Manhattan%20hush%20money%20trial%20with%20attorney%20Emil%20Bove.%3Cp%3EReuters%2FJane%20Rosenberg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBove%20appeared%20to%20have%20one%20main%20mission%20in%20cross-examining%20Davidson%20%E2%80%94%20to%20create%20distance%20between%20Trump%20and%20his%20campaign%20on%20one%20side%2C%20and%20the%20lawyer's%20wheeling%20and%20dealing%20on%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou've%20never%20met%20President%20Trump%2C%20correct%3F%26quot%3B%20Bove%20asked%20Davidson%2C%20as%20his%20very%20first%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNever%2C%26quot%3B%20Davidson%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20Tuesday%20was%20the%20first%20time%20that%20you've%20been%20in%20the%20same%20room%20as%20him%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20Bove%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20true%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20witness%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou've%20never%20spoken%20to%20President%20Trump%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNever%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EScandals%20and%20money%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20Bove%20amped%20up%20his%20attack%2C%20with%20a%20series%20of%20questions%20suggesting%20that%20Davidson%2C%20who%20was%20a%20top%20source%20of%20stories%20for%20the%20Enquirer's%20editor%2C%20had%20made%20a%20career%20of%20shakedowns%20and%20scandal-mongering%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20was%20a%20victim%2C%20not%20an%20instigator%2C%20in%20any%20hush-money%20schemes%2C%20the%20line%20of%20questioning%20implied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20does%20the%20word%20'extortion'%20mean%20to%20you%3F%26quot%3B%20Bove%20asked%20Davidson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExtortion%20is%20the%20%E2%80%94%26quot%3B%20Davidson%20fumbled.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20obtaining%20of%20property%20by%20threat%20of%20fear%20or%20force%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20were%20negotiating%20on%20behalf%20of%20Ms.%20McDougal%20and%20on%20be