0New%20York%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66340b0a0dfb1341e9022345%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221429%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETanya%20Brown%2C%20Denise%20Brown%2C%20and%20Dominique%20Brown%20speak%20onstage%20during%20Variety's%20Power%20of%20Women%20event%20in%20New%20York%20on%20May%202%2C%202024.%3Cp%3EBryan%20Bedder%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENicole%20Brown%20Simpson's%20family%20is%20collaborating%20with%20Lifetime%20to%20create%20a%20new%20docuseries.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20series%20aims%20to%20provide%20Brown%20Simpson's%20own%20narrative%20in%20one%20of%20history's%20most%20notorious%20crimes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHer%20family%20has%20been%20dedicated%20to%20addressing%20domestic%20violence%20issues.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20of%20the%20late%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fif-i-did-it-how-oj-simpson-2016-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENicole%20Brown%20Simpson%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20determined%20to%20rewrite%20the%20narrative%20and%20finally%20tell%20her%20story%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they're%20getting%20help%20from%20Lifetime%20with%20a%20new%20docuseries%20detailing%20her%20life%20and%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELifetime%20announced%20Thursday%20that%20%26quot%3BThe%20Life%20and%20Murder%20of%20Nicole%20Brown%20Simpson%26quot%3B%20will%20premiere%20on%20the%20network%20on%20June%201%20in%20a%20two-night%20event.%20The%20docuseries%20details%20the%20late%20mom's%20life%20and%20%26quot%3Bprovides%20an%20opportunity%20for%20Nicole's%20own%20narrative%20and%20voice%20to%20be%20heard%20in%20one%20of%20the%20most%20notorious%20crimes%20and%20trials%20in%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20press%20release%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201994%2C%20Simpson%20was%20killed%20alongside%20her%20friend%2C%20Ronald%20Goldman.%20Her%20ex-husband%2C%20former%20NFL%20player%20OJ%20Simpson%2C%20was%20accused%20and%20later%20acquitted%20of%20the%20crime%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fo-j-simpson-trial-photos-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehighly%20publicized%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20year%20later.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20honorees%20took%20the%20stage%20at%20Variety's%20Women%20of%20Power%20Event%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20Simpson's%20sisters%20spoke%20about%20her%20enduring%20legacy%20and%20how%20they're%20still%20%26quot%3Bheartbroken%26quot%3B%20from%20her%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20kind%20of%20a%20mixed%20emotion.%20As%20heartbroken%20as%20I%20am%20because%20we%20lost%20Nicole%20almost%2030%20years%20ago%20this%20June%2C%20we're%20here%20to%20celebrate%20all%20of%20these%20incredible%20women%20that%20do%20so%20much%20incredible%20work%20in%20their%20areas%20of%20expertise%2C%26quot%3B%20Denise%20Brown%20said%20onstage%20at%20the%20Cooper%20Hewitt%20Smithsonian%20Design%20Museum%20flanked%20by%20her%20two%20sisters%2C%20Tanya%20and%20Dominique.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Simpson's%20death%2C%20Brown%20said%20her%20family%20has%20been%20dedicated%20to%20the%20cause%20of%20domestic%20violence%20in%20many%20arenas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20really%20happy%20to%20see%20men%20in%20this%20audience%20because%20I%20truly%20believe%E2%80%A6it%20affects%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20the%20issue.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%20women.%20It%20affects%20the%20entire%20family.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNicole%20endured%20incredible%20pain%2C%20and%20through%20that%20pain%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20protect%20her%20children.%20She%20was%20able%20to%20be%20there%20for%20her%20children.%20She%20walked%20away%20from%20her%20abuser%2C%26quot%3B%20Denise%20Brown%20added.%20%26quot%3BShe%20was%20a%20daughter.%20She%20was%20a%20sister.%20She%20was%20a%20mother.%20She%20was%20a%20friend.%20She%20was%20a%20woman%20whose%20life%20was%20tragically%20cut%20short.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt