sed%20after%20finding%20it%20especially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-got-adhd-diagnosis-after-quarantine-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edifficult%20to%20parent%20with%20ADHD%20symptoms%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20something%20Philipps%20related%20to.%20Struggling%20to%20balance%20her%20work%20and%20childcare%20responsibilities%20made%20her%20feel%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bnever%20good%20enough%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bfailing%20in%20so%20many%20different%20avenues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhilipps%20shared%20how%20an%20ADHD%20diagnosis%20in%20adulthood%20helped%20her%20find%20treatment%20options%20that%20work%20for%20her%2C%20as%20well%20as%20newfound%20self-acceptance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPhilipps%20was%20previously%20diagnosed%20with%20ADHD%20as%20a%20child%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPhilipps%20said%20she%20was%20first%20diagnosed%20with%20ADHD%20when%20she%20was%20about%20seven%20or%20eight%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20diagnosis%20that%20apparently%20no%20one%20in%20my%20family%20really%20remembered%2C%26quot%3B%20Philipps%20said%2C%20save%20the%20elementary%20school%20medical%20records%20that%20her%20mom%20held%20on%20to.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20Philipps%20was%20briefly%20put%20on%20a%20medication%20she%20didn't%20like%20and%20hadn't%20thought%20about%20having%20ADHD%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20her%20symptoms%20persisted%20from%20her%20childhood%20through%20her%2020s%20and%2030s.%20Her%20main%20ones%20included%20an%20%26quot%3Binability%20to%20complete%20tasks%2C%20trouble%20focusing%2C%20literally%20walking%20into%20rooms%20and%20not%20remembering%20why%20you%20walked%20into%20the%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20Philipps%20said.%20%26quot%3BOften%20starting%20many%20different%20projects%20and%20leaving%20them%20sort%20of%20half%20done%2C%20double-booking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20women%20diagnosed%20with%20ADHD%2C%20Philipps%20had%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C