Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20take%20the%20Pacific%20Intertie%20%E2%80%94%20a%20highway%20of%20transmission%20lines%20that%20carry%20hydropower%20from%20the%20Columbia%20River%20all%20the%20way%20down%20to%20Southern%20California.%20The%20system%20may%20need%20to%20send%20power%20in%20the%20other%20direction%20more%20often%20as%20solar%20energy%20proliferates%20in%20the%20state's%20south.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20a%20cold%20snap%20up%20north.%20It%20was%20relatively%20sunny%20down%20south%2C%20and%20suddenly%20power%20was%20flowing%20the%20other%20direction%2C%26quot%3B%20Schneider%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20software%20and%20automated%20equipment%20to%20handle%20that%20process%20could%20make%20it%20much%20more%20efficient%20and%20help%20the%20system%20quickly%20adapt%20to%20unforeseen%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20smart%20grid%20is%20designed%20to%20do%20more%20than%20one%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20start%20to%20see%20more%20things%20like%20that%2C%20where%20the%20system%20was%20designed%20to%20do%20X%2C%20and%20we're%20seeing%20ABCDEFG%2C%26quot%3B%20Schneider%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESmart%20grids%20can%20bring%20huge%20economic%20benefits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22illustration%20of%20smiling%20houses%20with%20solar%20panels%20and%20wind%20turbines%20and%20cars%20plugged%20into%20electric%20charging%20stations%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6633fd080dfb1341e90218b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESmart%20meters%20on%20homes%20can%20help%20efficiently%20manage%20electricity%20use%2C%20and%20the%20smart%20grid%20can%20help%20integrate%20renewables%20and%20EVs.%3Cp%3ETiago%20Majuelos%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20Congress%20knows%20the%20nation%20needs%20a%20smart%20grid.%20In%202007%2C%20it%20directed%20the%20Department%20of%20Energy%20to%20start%20doling%20out%20grants%20to%20make%20it%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20program%20that%20gave%20EPB%20a%20boost%2C%20and%20it%20has%20spent%20billions%20on%20smart-grid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-build-infrastructure-transportation-housing-regulation-environment-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einfrastructure%20nationwide%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20seems%20like%20the%20kick%20start%20worked.%20In%202020%2C%20the%20department%20estimated%20that%20smart-grid%20investments%20would%20rise%20to%20%2416.4%20billion%20annually%20by%202026%20%E2%80%94%20compared%20with%20about%20%246.4%20billion%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20a%20smart%20grid%20requires%20a%20big%20up-front%20investment%2C%20it%20can%20save%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20down%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22utility%20worker%20in%20jeans%20sweatshirt%20and%20hardhat%20sits%20and%20controls%20a%20long%20arm%20that's%20raising%20a%20large%20rectangular%20metal%20device%20toward%20power%20lines%20above%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6633d7470dfb1341e901f5cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20expenses%20of%20installing%20smart%20grid%20technology%20paid%20off%20for%20Chattanooga.%3Cp%3EEPB%20of%20Chattanooga%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20of%20EPB's%20smart%20grid%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20valued%20the%20benefits%20to%20each%20Hamilton%20County%20resident%20at%20about%20%24646%20a%20year%20in%20the%20project's%20first%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20the%20project%20created%20more%20than%209%2C500%20jobs%2C%20helped%20attract%20new%20businesses%20with%20cost-efficient%20energy%20and%20high-speed%20internet%2C%20and%20kept%20customers'%20electric%20bills%20lower%20than%20they%20would%20have%20