t%20I%20did%20not%20like%20that%20job%20or%20any%20other%20job%20in%20particular%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhavesh%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20a%20childhood%20episode%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20my%20father%20would%20take%20me%20to%20his%20workplace%2C%20I%20saw%20him%20obey%20the%20rules%20and%20orders%20of%20others.%20He%20would%20work%20under%20so%20much%20stress.%20I%20aspired%20to%20a%20life%20of%20freedom.%20Also%2C%20I%20was%20afraid%20to%20leave%20my%20home.%20My%20mother%20would%20jokingly%20warn%20me%20to%20send%20me%20to%20a%20hostel%20if%20I%20did%20any%20mischief.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20appeared%20for%20the%20government%20examination%20in%202017%20but%20failed%20to%20clear%20it.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20my%20family%20was%20sad%2C%20I%20was%20secretly%20happy%20that%20I%20failed%20the%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20also%20dropped%20out%20of%20his%20BSc%20in%20his%20second%20year.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20started%20taunting%20me%20that%20I%20would%20either%20end%20up%20in%20farming%20or%20labour%20jobs.%20My%20father%20was%20very%20angry%20at%20me%20and%20forcefully%20enrolled%20me%20in%20an%20engineering%20college.%20But%20I%20dropped%20out%20of%20college%20after%20a%20month%20as%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FKasutam-2-1713339469.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20the%20help%20of%20his%20mother%2C%20Bhavesh%20started%20preparing%20A2%20Cow%20Ghee%2C%20which%20is%20produced%20by%20extracting%20nutritious%20milk%20from%20desi%20cows.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FKasutam-2-1713339469.jpg%2