%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20his%20peers%20succeeded%2C%20Bhavesh%20was%20jobless%20and%20clueless%20about%20what%20to%20do%20in%20life.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhavesh%20hired%20a%20techie%20from%20Bengaluru%20to%20design%20a%20website%20for%20his%20online%20business.%20As%20he%20lacked%20savings%2C%20he%20took%20a%20loan%20of%20Rs%2021%2C000%20from%20his%20friends%20for%20this%20purpose.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20after%20the%20website%20was%20designed%2C%20I%20did%20not%20get%20any%20orders.%20The%20techie%20told%20me%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20post%20product%20photos%20to%20get%20orders.%20I%20did%20not%20know%20how%20to%20post%20pictures%20and%20courier%20products.%20I%20got%20afraid%20and%20the%20website%20shut%20even%20before%20starting%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20this%20incident%2C%20Bhavesh%20knew%20he%20had%20to%20click%20captivating%20pictures%20of%20his%20product.%20For%20this%2C%20he%20placed%20an%20online%20order%20for%20two%20glass%20jars%20and%20a%20cellotape.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20had%20given%20me%20Rs%203%2C000%20to%20get%20my%20driving%20licence%20but%20I%20secretly%20used%20this%20amount%20to%20buy%20glass%20jars.%20By%20this%20time%2C%20my%20family%20had%20no%20idea%20about%20my%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsing%20WhatsApp%2C%20he%20made%20catalogues%20and%20started%20advertising%20his%20brand%20on%20related%20YouTube%20videos%20that%20talked%20about%20the%20benefits%20of%20consuming%20pure%20ghee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFrom%20morning%20till%20night%2C%20I%20advertised%20my%20ghee%20products%20by%20adding%20comments%20about%20them%20along%20with%20my%20contact%20details%20on%20several%20videos.%20Within%20a%20week%2C%20I%20got%20my%20first%20order.%20I%20earned%20Rs%201%2C125!%20This%20was%20my%20first%20incom